    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000872/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """This course teaches methods to perform usability evaluation, experimental design and to statistically analyse the results. Different evaluation methods will be introduced for different tasks, user groups, and performed in a lab environment as well as in field.
Additionally, this course place the user in the centre of the evaluation, including vulnerable groups as participants with disabilities."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/elena.villalba%40upm.es> ;
